profile:
I am a local service and garage door installer for the Barrie and surrounding area for 18 years. Customer satisfaction is a key factor for myself and my business. 

Please feel free to either email or phone  for any day to day concerns with your doors, or for any quotes towards new ones. 

We provide removal and disposal of existing garage doors, and provide a selection of newer styles in a variety of colours for your home. 

Also available are different styles of garage door openers. We offer maintenance on all doors and openers to prevent unnecessary problems for you during the changing seasons.

Roly's Garage Doors and Openers

Since 2009, Canadoor Door Systems has been bringing professionalism to the garage door industry. To ensure we perform every job to the highest standard, whether you need a garage door repair or installation, our technicians undergo a rigorous training process until we’re confident they are ready to enter the field.

We provide service across Ontario, with showrooms in Barrie, Bolton, Sudbury and Thunder Bay, where you can meet our team and browse our selection of garage doors. Whether you’re a homeowner in need of a garage door repair, new installation or a business looking for preventative maintenance on your commercial properties, we can help.

profile:
Georgian Door & Gate is a garage door specialist for residential, commercial, agricultural and industrial applications, proudly serving the Barrie area. We would love for you to visit our showroom at 56 Churchill Dr., Barrie, ON. There, our team can give you personalized advice in purchasing a garage door, an installation that meets the highest industry standards, and unequalled after-sales service thanks to our maintenance and repair program.

Our full range of products also includes electric garage door openers as well as many other accessories to go with your garage door. Think of us when it comes to buying, installing or repairing any type of garage door.

We have 3 employees ready to give you the fastest service in the industry. Our showroom is located at 56 Churchill Dr., Barrie, ON and is open Monday to Friday from 8:00 AM to 4:00 PM.

I invite you to come and visit us, and on behalf of our entire team, I thank you for considering our company.

Bob English
Manager

profile:
Our Company was founded by Peter Vriezema in 1977 and his son Matt joined the team in 1997, twenty three later.  We know doors, inside and out.  We install and supply products ranging from steel insulated doors, roll up doors, openers, dock seals, dock bumpers, custom cedar carriage house doors, and we can repair any problem you can come up with.  We have a work boat which allows us to do boat house doors on Georgian Bay on the mainland or any island. 

But the real reason we are still in business today, is the fact that we are honest, hard-working, conscientious business people ready to meet your garage door needs.  We are prompt and stand behind the products that we supply.  We take our warranty program very seriously. 

We are located in Midhurst but have a service area from Collingwood down to Alliston and everywhere in between.  We invite you to call us at (705) 721-7909 for any garage door need. 

We look forward to working with you in the near future.  You won't regret your decision. 

Matt and Peter Vriezema, owners Vriezema Overhead Doors
